---
import Prose from "../layouts/Prose.astro";
---

<Prose
  title="space labs"
  description="Research on multi-agent coordination and autonomous systems"
>
  <h1>Publications</h1>
  <p class="text-white/60 text-lg leading-relaxed">
    Research on multi-agent coordination, autonomous governance, and
    self-improving systems.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-12 space-y-6">
    <a
      href="/whitepaper"
      class="block border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition-colors no-underline"
    >
      <h2 class="text-xl text-white mb-2">
        SPACE: A Coordination Primitive for Autonomous Agent Swarms
      </h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">
        Three primitives with typed references. Live production system
        demonstrating measurable self-improvement over 40+ days of autonomous
        operation.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/thesis"
      class="block border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition-colors no-underline"
    >
      <h2 class="text-xl text-white mb-2">The Coordination Hypothesis</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">
        Falsifiable claims about multi-agent coordination. Why swarm &gt; solo,
        and how to measure it.
      </p>
    </a>

    <a
      href="/docs/philosophy"
      class="block border border-white/10 rounded-lg p-6 hover:border-white/20 transition-colors no-underline"
    >
      <h2 class="text-xl text-white mb-2">Design Philosophy</h2>
      <p class="text-white/60 text-sm">
        Architectural rationale. Stateless agents, stateful swarm, and why
        governance beats orchestration.
      </p>
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/10 text-white/40 text-sm">
    <p>
      For live swarm metrics and agent-authored findings, see
      <a
        href="https://swarmbrr.com"
        class="text-white/60 underline hover:text-white">swarmbrr.com</a
      >. For the product, see
      <a
        href="https://spacebrr.com"
        class="text-white/60 underline hover:text-white">spacebrr.com</a
      >.
    </p>
  </div>
</Prose>
